    "html": "<html lang=\"en\"><head>\n\t<meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n\t<!-- style sheet that has stuff that is uniform on most pages-->\n\t<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"/Physics/sitewide/standardstylings.css\">\n\n\t<!-- style sheet that has stuff that is unique to this program only-->\n\t<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"stylings.css\">\n\n\t<!-- loads JQuery into memory-->\n\t<script src=\"https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.7.1/jquery.min.js\"></script>\n\n\t<!-- loads javascript for standard things on site-->\n\t<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"/Physics/sitewide/standardjavascript.js\"></script>\n\n\t<!-- loads javascript for this program only-->\n\t<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"javascript.js\"></script>\n\n\t<title>Car Stopping Distance</title>\n</head>\n\n\n\n<body onload=\"initialize();\">\n<div id=\"FullPage\">\n\t<div id=\"MainBody\">\n\t\t<div id=\"ProgramTitle\" class=\"Titles\">Car Stopping Distance</div>\n\t\t<div id=\"OverviewSection\">\n\t\t\t<div id=\"LabDirections\" class=\"Directions\">\n\t\t\t\tIn this problem a car is traveling down a country road when the driver remembers they left their smart watch at home.  The driver is going to jam on their brakes to stop the car and you need to predict how far the car will travel while stopping and how much time will be required to stop the car<p>Click begin to start working on problem\n\t\t\t</p></div>\n\t\t\t<div id=\"PersonName\" class=\"Directions\"><span id=\"WordName\">Name:</span> <input type=\"text\" id=\"StudentName\" class=\"NameInput\"></div>\n\t\t\t<img id=\"OverviewPicture\" src=\"images/OverviewPicture.png\" alt=\"Car Stopping Distance\">\n\t\t\t<div id=\"BeginButton\" class=\"Button\" onclick=\"LoadIt()\">Begin</div>\n\t\t\t<div id=\"AvailableLanguages\">\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"LanguageTitle\" class=\"LittleDirections\" onclick=\"ShowLanguages()\">See Available Languages</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"LanguageDropDown\"></div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div id=\"LabSection\">\n\t\t\t<div id=\"DrawingSectionOne\">\n\t\t\t\t<canvas id=\"CanvasOne\" width=\"925\" height=\"600\">\n\t\t\t\t\tYour browser does not support HTML 5.0 Canvas...get a better browser!!!\n\t\t\t\t</canvas>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"SystemMessage\" class=\"Directions\">A car is traveling down a country road when the driver needs to suddenly stop the car.  Based on the information below, how much time is required to stop the car and how much groudn will the car cover while actively braking?</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"SpaceForAnswer\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"AnswerTitle\" class=\"Directions\">Enter Answers</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"DirectionsforSub\" class=\"LittleDirections\">Don't include units</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"FormArea\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"FormRow\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"TextBox\"><span id=\"Q1\" class=\"FormText\">Time (s):</span></div><div class=\"AnswerBox\"><input type=\"text\" id=\"A1\" class=\"FormInputs\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"FormRow\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"TextBox\"><span id=\"Q2\" class=\"FormText\">Displacement (m):</span></div><div class=\"AnswerBox\"><input type=\"text\" id=\"A2\" class=\"FormInputs\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"SubmitButton\" class=\"Button\" onclick=\"StartMotion()\">Check</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</div>\n\n\n</div></body></html>",
